Sentencas: conductor Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-delta (BZCY7) as an electrolyte material for solid-oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) is investigated.
Titulo: Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ as an electrolyte for low-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrolyte material exhibits ionic conductivities (see figure) among the highest known for electrolytes viable for SOFC applications, and the chemical and thermal stability of BZCY7 appear adequate under a range of SOFC operating conditions.
Titulo: Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ as an electrolyte for low-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Several BZCY7-based single cells are fabricated using a modified dry-pressing method and show encouraging performance characteristics.
Titulo: Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ as an electrolyte for low-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells
